text: Shawn Thierry is an American politician. She is a Democratic member of the Texas House of Representatives, representing the 146th District. She won the November 2016 general election and was sworn into office on January 10, 2017. Thierry was an unsuccessful candidate for the 57th Civil District Court in 2010. ==References== ==External links== * Campaign website * State legislative page * Shawn Thierry at the Texas Tribune Category:Living people Category:Members of the Texas House of Representatives Category:21st-century American politicians Category:Texas Democrats Category:Texas lawyers Category:Howard University alumni Category:Thurgood Marshall School of Law alumni Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
